# SpecAI Architecture

Inspired by @piotrostr’s Listen toolkit, SpecAI’s architecture optimizes healthcare workflows:

- **Rig Agent Kit**: Configures modes (Nurse, Patient, Chatbot) via Rig (https://github.com/0xPlaygrounds/rig).
- **Workflow Pipeline**: Prioritizes tasks (Listen-inspired, @piotrostr).
- **Data Service**: Streams simulated vitals (Tidepool) and EHR (OpenEMR).
- **Epic FHIR API**: Simulated logs/data (requires live integration).
- **Solana ARC**: Blockchain logging with SHA-256.

See README flowchart for details.
